	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The skinny is missing some necessary information:
<br />
<br />"Y Scroll" increments at PPU cycle 251
<br />"X Scroll" resets at PPU cycle 257
<br />"Scroll Reset" (the V=T) happens at cycle 304 of the pre-render scanline

		

		</td>
